		<h1> It's important to note that these are not in order of release date or anyhting, just the order I added them in. </h1> 
		<h2> Here are links to websites that have adapters or kits for modifications. Best way to get guitars would be either to get the riffmaster, look at facebook marketplace, or go ebay hunting for a good deal.</h2>
		<h3>
			<ul>
